WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.030 --> 00:00:02.745
MCP Server gives AI clients

2
00:00:02.765 --> 00:00:04.615
a structured way to work

3
00:00:04.635 --> 00:00:06.260
with TYPO3. In the backend,

4
00:00:06.280 --> 00:00:07.910
an administrator can see the

5
00:00:07.930 --> 00:00:09.745
connection address, check its status,

6
00:00:09.765 --> 00:00:10.695
and manage access.

7
00:00:10.715 --> 00:00:13.780
Connected tools can read pages,

8
00:00:13.800 --> 00:00:15.940
records, and files, while changes

9
00:00:15.960 --> 00:00:17.513
are prepared in a workspace

10
00:00:17.533 --> 00:00:19.120
for review. The same actions

11
00:00:19.140 --> 00:00:20.625
are available from the command

12
00:00:20.645 --> 00:00:22.445
line. The feature page explains

13
00:00:22.465 --> 00:00:24.310
setup and safeguards.
